schema:description: 20' x 32' - similar to Agricultural Engineering Division standard plans. Contains 3 ton refrigeration plant and cold room, boiler and concrete sterilizer as shown, concrete wash trap and other standard equipment. Clay block secured from seconds pile in cannon yards - Sac at $45 thousand. Milking machine included in refrigeration machinery room and run from same motor.
